{
  "id": "RAW_7356e0",
  "title": "借助 CSS 实现自适应屏幕边缘的 tooltip",
  "url": "https://juejin.cn/post/7538833818543767579",
  "date": "2025-08-17 05:23:39",
  "author": "XboxYan",
  "siteName": "掘金本周最热",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div class=\"article-viewer markdown-body result\">\n   <blockquote>\n    <p>欢迎关注我的公众号：<strong>前端侦探</strong></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p><code>tooltip</code>是一个非常常见的交互，一般用于补充文案说明。比如下面这种（蓝色边框表示屏幕边缘）</p>\n   <p><img src=\"https://p6-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/6df37fb3052f4a029f0bd80a6de66c4f~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAgWGJveFlhbg==:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1756013018&amp;x-signature=pQGl6ow6Fr5Ap5WXRXM%2FBbOkiZo%3D\" alt=\"image-20250523223912070\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"medium-zoom-image\"></p>\n   <p>通常<code>tooltip</code>都会有一个固定的方向，比如<code>top</code>表示垂直居中向上。</p>\n   <p>但是，如果提示文案比较多，提示区域右比较靠近屏幕边缘，就可能出现这种情况</p>\n   <p><img src=\"https://p6-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/5161cdace05740cbaa0e4f0813efadb6~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAgWGJveFlhbg==:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1756013018&amp;x-signature=fLgjk6cgsffbpv7%2FUcNTiZ6B3R8%3D\" alt=\"image-20250523224309231\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"medium-zoom-image\"></p>\n   <p>直接超出屏幕！这很显然是不能接受的。</p>\n   <p>你可能会想到改变一下对齐方向，比如<code>top-right</code>，但是这里的文案可能是不固定的，也就是会出现这样</p>\n   <p><img src=\"https://p6-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/bbb530396e6b4d0886386fc964377e96~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAgWGJveFlhbg==:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1756013018&amp;x-signature=skclE83DGwDGOf0HLlMOvXn%2FzTg%3D\" alt=\"image-20250523224706671\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"medium-zoom-image\"></p>\n   <p>嗯...感觉无论怎么对齐都会有局限。那么如何解决呢？一起看看吧</p>\n   <h2 data-id=\"heading-0\">一、理想中的自适应对齐</h2>\n   <p>我们先想想，最完美的对齐是什么样的。</p>\n   <p>其实没那么复杂，就分两种情况，一个居左，一个居右</p>\n   <h2 data-id=\"heading-1\">1.居左</h2>\n   <p>正常情况下，就是垂直居中朝上</p>\n   <p><img src=\"https://p6-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/44af23b7cc7447f8a8b2598daac7f37f~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAgWGJveFlhbg==:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1756013018&amp;x-signature=Yl6l2yDbk%2By7SkgTNcxu4SisL5w%3D\" alt=\"image-20250523225707868\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"medium-zoom-image\"></p>\n   <p>如果提示文本比较多，那就靠左贴近文本容器对齐</p>\n   <p><img src=\"https://p6-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/f95e65217374434093db2f0f04cb824c~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAgWGJveFlhbg==:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1756013018&amp;x-signature=xoCxuXXHkIaTjQlYwN6AukjFHbM%3D\" alt=\"image-20250523225826347\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"medium-zoom-image\"></p>\n   <p>如果提示文本继续增加，那就整行换行，并且不超过文本容器</p>\n   <p><img src=\"https://p6-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/8f7cbbf5ff464292bd58671263c2b569~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAgWGJveFlhbg==:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1756013018&amp;x-signature=GVLbi%2FS1sRur%2FuhFmctFcCmgjfM%3D\" alt=\"image-20250523230041333\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"medium-zoom-image\"></p>\n   <h2 data-id=\"heading-2\">2. 居右</h2>\n   <p>正常情况下，也是垂直居中朝上</p>\n   <p><img src=\"https://p6-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/642d00136150419c8b16fc128ec0931e~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAgWGJveFlhbg==:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1756013018&amp;x-signature=SaouwuOABrnm7AWVAfZ5fwEPAyM%3D\" alt=\"image-20250523230849249\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"medium-zoom-image\"></p>\n   <p>如果提示文本比较多，那就靠右贴近文本容器对齐</p>\n   <p><img src=\"https://p6-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/d5fce3a8ff4544e0b1a1d448fb5293f2~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAgWGJveFlhbg==:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1756013018&amp;x-signature=ycraYB8nXKGn%2B4utcJRFe7uN0TA%3D\" alt=\"image-20250523230936187\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"medium-zoom-image\"></p>\n   <p>如果提示文本继续增加，也是整行换行，并且不超过文本容器</p>\n   <p><img src=\"https://p6-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/c38d57c69f294062aefbbf50824f25cf~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAgWGJveFlhbg==:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1756013018&amp;x-signature=onSswmIWj7AuhoI8AL4NKLJPsts%3D\" alt=\"image-20250523231035167\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"medium-zoom-image\"></p>\n   <p>那么如何实现这样的对齐方式呢？</p>\n   <h2 data-id=\"heading-3\">二、左自适应对齐的思路</h2>\n   <p>我们先看第一种情况，看似好像有3种对齐方式，而且还要监测是否到了边界，好像挺复杂。其实换个角度，其实是这样一种规则</p>\n   <ol>\n    <li>当内容较少时，居中对齐</li>\n    <li>当内容较多时，居左对齐</li>\n    <li>当内容多到换行时，有一个最大宽度</li>\n   </ol>\n   <p>既然涉及到了对齐，那就有对齐的容器和被对齐的对象。</p>\n   <p>我们可以想象一个虚拟容器，以对齐中心（下图问号图标）向两边扩展，一直到边界处，如下所示（淡蓝色区域）</p>\n   <p><img src=\"https://p6-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/50d462d2a45b4dc7a18ae11452f59271~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAgWGJveFlhbg==:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1756013018&amp;x-signature=MffO8Hmvdyk3YrFJaEny6d8rT0E%3D\" alt=\"image-20250523233837924\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"medium-zoom-image\"></p>\n   <p>假设<code>HTML</code>如下</p>\n   <pre><code class=\"hljs language-html code-block-extension-codeShowNum\" lang=\"html\"><span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"1\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">span</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"tooltip\"</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">title</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"提示\"</span>&gt;</span><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">span</span>&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre>\n   <p>当气泡文本比较少时，可以通过文本对齐实现居中，气泡可以直接通过伪元素实现</p>\n   <pre><code class=\"hljs language-css code-block-extension-codeShowNum\" lang=\"css\"><span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"1\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.tooltip</span>{</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"2\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">width</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">50px</span>; <span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*虚拟容器宽度，暂时先固定 */</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"3\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">text-align</span>:center;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"4\">}</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"5\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.tooltip</span><span class=\"hljs-selector-pseudo\">::before</span>{</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"6\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">content</span>: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">attr</span>(title);</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"7\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">display</span>: inline-block;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"8\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">#fff</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"9\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">background-color</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">#000</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"10\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">padding</span>: .<span class=\"hljs-number\">5em</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">1em</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"11\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">border-radius</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">8px</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"12\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">box-sizing</span>: border-box;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"13\">}</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"14\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*居中箭头*/</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"15\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.tooltip</span><span class=\"hljs-selector-pseudo\">::after</span>{</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"16\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">content</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">''</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"17\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">position</span>: absolute;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"18\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">width</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">1em</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"19\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">height</span>: .<span class=\"hljs-number\">6em</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"20\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">background</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">#000</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"21\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">clip-path</span>: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">polygon</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100%</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">50%</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">100%</span>);</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"22\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">top</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"23\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">left</span>:<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"24\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">right</span>:<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"25\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">margin</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span> auto;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"26\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">transform</span>: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">translateY</span>(-<span class=\"hljs-number\">150%</span>)</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"27\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n   <p>使用文本居中，也就是<code>text-align: center</code>有个好处，当文本不超过容器时，居中展示，就如同上图展示一样。</p>\n   <p>当文本比较多时，默认会换行，效果如下</p>\n   <p><img src=\"https://p6-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/d1f973b23e2a4b938a272cccd6cab603~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAgWGJveFlhbg==:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1756013018&amp;x-signature=4pCX%2FSbaRO533Fhd5AYzQnN1Rqw%3D\" alt=\"image-20250524112135696\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"medium-zoom-image\"></p>\n   <p>这样应该很好理解吧。</p>\n   <p>我们需要气泡里的文本在多行时居左，可以直接给气泡设置居左对齐</p>\n   <pre><code class=\"hljs language-css code-block-extension-codeShowNum\" lang=\"css\"><span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"1\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.tooltip</span><span class=\"hljs-selector-pseudo\">::before</span>{</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"2\">  <span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*...*/</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"3\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">text-align</span>: left;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"4\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n   <p>效果如下</p>\n   <p><img src=\"https://p6-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/c38139d176a749c8b02525ea4a5fc203~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAgWGJveFlhbg==:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1756013018&amp;x-signature=INq3N5sN1L5k%2FBzK2qrICHOXTag%3D\" alt=\"image-20250524112333960\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"medium-zoom-image\"></p>\n   <p>这样就实现了单行居中，多行居左的效果了。</p>\n   <p>现在还有一个问题，如何在气泡文本较多时，不被对齐容器束缚呢？</p>\n   <p>首先可以想到的是禁止换行，也就是</p>\n   <pre><code class=\"hljs language-css code-block-extension-codeShowNum\" lang=\"css\"><span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"1\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.tooltip</span><span class=\"hljs-selector-pseudo\">::before</span>{</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"2\">  <span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*...*/</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"3\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">white-space</span>: nowrap</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"4\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n   <p>这样在文本不超过一行时确实可以</p>\n   <p><img src=\"https://p6-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/38ea713bd73545a4b65970145ac41e7e~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAgWGJveFlhbg==:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1756013018&amp;x-signature=%2Bh7mkgjBXqHW7pFfD2yiKFaTDH8%3D\" alt=\"image-20250524112641734\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"medium-zoom-image\"></p>\n   <p>看，已经突破了容器束缚。但是文本继续增加时，也会出现无法换行的问题</p>\n   <p><img src=\"https://p6-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/1157e2e261eb4d72b0bdddbfc351d1c9~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAgWGJveFlhbg==:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1756013018&amp;x-signature=6eIjUYWXvbgDGBVY%2BjsbC0KKha8%3D\" alt=\"image-20250524112800984\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"medium-zoom-image\"></p>\n   <p>我们可以想一想，还有什么方式可以控制换行呢？</p>\n   <p>这里，我们需要设置宽度为<strong>最大内容宽度</strong>，相当于文本有多少，文本容器就有多宽</p>\n   <pre><code class=\"hljs language-css code-block-extension-codeShowNum\" lang=\"css\"><span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"1\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.tooltip</span><span class=\"hljs-selector-pseudo\">::before</span>{</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"2\">  <span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*...*/</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"3\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">width</span>: max-content</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"4\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n   <p>看似好像和不换行一样</p>\n   <p><img src=\"https://p6-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/17a12dedd1e748c389895e85f19111ca~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAgWGJveFlhbg==:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1756013018&amp;x-signature=TTlkNxt7cIB%2BiEpkIicSs9lW28o%3D\" alt=\"image-20250524112800984\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"medium-zoom-image\"></p>\n   <p>实则不然，我们并没用禁止换行。只要给一个最大宽度，立马就换行了</p>\n   <pre><code class=\"hljs language-css code-block-extension-codeShowNum\" lang=\"css\"><span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"1\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.tooltip</span><span class=\"hljs-selector-pseudo\">::before</span>{</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"2\">  <span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*...*/</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"3\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">width</span>: max-content；</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"4\">  max-width: <span class=\"hljs-number\">300px</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"5\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n   <p>效果如下</p>\n   <p><img src=\"https://p6-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/dcb545ca4654469c83e13d7a9290d206~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAgWGJveFlhbg==:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1756013018&amp;x-signature=DzkftLTaafwp4qlmpW0IOkXCdvw%3D\" alt=\"image-20250524113318010\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"medium-zoom-image\"></p>\n   <p>是不是几乎实现了我们想要的效果了？</p>\n   <p>不过，这里涉及了两个需要动态计算的宽度，一个是虚拟容器宽度，还有一个是外层最大宽度，</p>\n   <p><img src=\"https://p6-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/0ad67dd440514173be26bdee5e561ba8~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAgWGJveFlhbg==:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1756013018&amp;x-signature=GI%2FOJUgH82jCz52zgslXJmY2sAM%3D\" alt=\"image-20250524152008282\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"medium-zoom-image\"></p>\n   <p>下面看如何实现</p>\n   <h2 data-id=\"heading-4\">三、借助JS计算所需宽度</h2>\n   <p>现如今，外层的最大宽度倒是可以通过容器查询获得，但内部的虚拟容器宽度还无法直接获取，只能借助<code>JS</code>了。</p>\n   <p>不过我们这里可以先只计算左侧偏移，也就是一半的宽度</p>\n   <p><img src=\"https://p6-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/f7e88169790949879e3e3ff7fcc2a62e~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAgWGJveFlhbg==:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1756013018&amp;x-signature=xiBb1OYcwgzaOGB02JzZ67b0jJw%3D\" alt=\"image-20250524155257344\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"medium-zoom-image\"></p>\n   <p>具体实现如下</p>\n   <pre><code class=\"hljs language-js code-block-extension-codeShowNum\" lang=\"js\"><span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"1\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">//问号中心到左侧距离</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"2\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> x = <span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">this</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">offsetLeft</span> - <span class=\"hljs-number\">8</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"3\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 问号的宽度</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"4\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> w = <span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">this</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">clientWidth</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"5\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 外层整行文本容器宽度</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"6\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> W = <span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">this</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">offsetParent</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">clientWidth</span> - <span class=\"hljs-number\">32</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"7\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 左侧偏移</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"8\"><span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">this</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">style</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">setProperty</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">'--x'</span>, x + <span class=\"hljs-string\">'px'</span>)</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"9\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 外层文本容器宽度（气泡最大宽度）</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"10\"><span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">this</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">style</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">setProperty</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">'--w'</span>, W + <span class=\"hljs-string\">'px'</span>)</span>\n</code></pre>\n   <p>然后给前面待定的宽度绑定这些变量就行了</p>\n   <pre><code class=\"hljs language-css code-block-extension-codeShowNum\" lang=\"css\"><span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"1\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.tooltip</span>{</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"2\">  <span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*...*/</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"3\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">width</span>: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">calc</span>(<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">var</span>(--x) * <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>);</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"4\">}</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"5\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.tooltip</span><span class=\"hljs-selector-pseudo\">::before</span>{</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"6\">  <span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*...*/</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"7\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">max-width</span>: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">var</span>(--w);</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"8\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n   <p>这样左侧就完全实现自适应了，无需实时计算，仅需初始化一次就好了</p>\n   <p><img alt=\"Kapture 2025-05-24 at 15.56.13转存失败，建议直接上传图片文件\" src=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"medium-zoom-image\"></p>\n   <h2 data-id=\"heading-5\">四、完全自适应对齐</h2>\n   <p>前面是左侧，那右侧如何判断呢？我们可以比较左侧距离的占比，如果超过一半，就表示现在是居右了</p>\n   <p>这里用一个属性表示</p>\n   <pre><code class=\"hljs language-js code-block-extension-codeShowNum\" lang=\"js\"><span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"1\"><span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">this</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">tooltip</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">dataset</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">left</span> = x/W &lt; <span class=\"hljs-number\">0.5</span> <span class=\"hljs-comment\">//是否居左</span></span>\n</code></pre>\n   <p>然后就右侧虚拟容器的宽度了，和左侧还有有点不一样</p>\n   <p><img src=\"https://p6-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/9ee47f53b3484544aea70fb5a9a6d836~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAgWGJveFlhbg==:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1756013018&amp;x-signature=Mv8LNCG66rVH0sUtRJfn564rp%2Bg%3D\" alt=\"image-20250524160146516\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"medium-zoom-image\"></p>\n   <p>前面我们已经算出了左侧距离，由于超过了一半，所以需要先减然后再乘以二</p>\n   <pre><code class=\"hljs language-css code-block-extension-codeShowNum\" lang=\"css\"><span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"1\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.tooltip</span><span class=\"hljs-selector-attr\">[data-left=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"false\"</span>]</span><span class=\"hljs-selector-pseudo\">::before</span>{</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"2\">  <span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*...*/</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"3\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">width</span>: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">calc</span>( (<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">var</span>(--w) - <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">var</span>(--x)) * <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>);</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"4\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">max-width</span>: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">var</span>(--w);</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"5\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n   <p>其实这里还是有个小问题的，当气泡文字比较长时，仍然是朝右突破了边界，如下所示</p>\n   <p><img src=\"https://p6-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/9a275676dab74bf6a1ff052a67e6419f~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAgWGJveFlhbg==:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1756013018&amp;x-signature=9p0LE9Zr1wqBoca3JqTxU1GOjF8%3D\" alt=\"image-20250524160531721\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"medium-zoom-image\"></p>\n   <p>这是因为默认的语言流向造成的（从左往右），解决这个问题也非常简单，仅需改变语言方向就可以了，要用到<code>direction:rtl</code>，如下</p>\n   <pre><code class=\"hljs language-css code-block-extension-codeShowNum\" lang=\"css\"><span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"1\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.tooltip</span><span class=\"hljs-selector-attr\">[data-left=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"false\"</span>]</span><span class=\"hljs-selector-pseudo\">::before</span>{</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"2\">  <span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*...*/</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"3\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">width</span>: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">calc</span>( (<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">var</span>(--w) - <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">var</span>(--x)) * <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>);</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"4\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">max-width</span>: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">var</span>(--w);</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"5\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">direction</span>: rtl;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"6\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n   <p>这样就完美了</p>\n   <p><img src=\"https://p6-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/ddca612725874d6c81892b9d1177fcbf~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAgWGJveFlhbg==:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1756013018&amp;x-signature=FxCa6Bz3TOyKgegQo1EQQ%2BFrYsI%3D\" alt=\"image-20250524160856055\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"medium-zoom-image\"></p>\n   <p>现在来看一下所有边界情况的演示</p>\n   <p><img src=\"https://p6-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/b8369cefbb52421682cbd4e73090259d~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAgWGJveFlhbg==:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1756013018&amp;x-signature=3D%2Ff%2B0Th3nDzZYNaGOr5Tj8bRv0%3D\" alt=\"Kapture 2025-05-24 at 16.10.06\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"medium-zoom-image\"></p>\n   <p>你也可以访问在线demo真实体验：<a href=\"https://link.juejin.cn?target=https%3A%2F%2Fcodepen.io%2Fxboxyan%2Fpen%2FQwLJwbN\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://codepen.io/xboxyan/pen/QwLJwbN\" ref=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">codepen.io/xboxyan/pen…</a></p>\n   <p>如果你是 vue3 项目，可以直接用这段封装好的组件（其实没几行代码，大部分自适应都是<code>CSS</code>完成的）</p>\n   <pre><code class=\"hljs language-js code-block-extension-codeShowNum\" lang=\"js\"><span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"1\">&lt;!-- 极度自适应的tooltips --&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"2\"><span class=\"xml\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">script</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">setup</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">lang</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"ts\"</span>&gt;</span><span class=\"javascript\"></span></span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"3\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> props = <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">defineProps</span>({</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"4\">  <span class=\"hljs-attr\">text</span>: <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">String</span>,</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"5\">  <span class=\"hljs-attr\">gap</span>: {</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"6\">    <span class=\"hljs-attr\">type</span>: <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Number</span>,</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"7\">    <span class=\"hljs-attr\">default</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">12</span>,</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"8\">  },</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"9\">})</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"10\"></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"11\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> show = <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">ref</span>(<span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>)</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"12\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> pos = <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">reactive</span>({</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"13\">  <span class=\"hljs-attr\">x</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>,</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"14\">  <span class=\"hljs-attr\">w</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>,</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"15\">  <span class=\"hljs-attr\">top</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>,</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"16\">  <span class=\"hljs-attr\">gap</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>,</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"17\">  <span class=\"hljs-attr\">isLeft</span>: <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>,</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"18\">})</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"19\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">click</span> = (<span class=\"hljs-params\">ev: MouseEvent</span>) =&gt; {</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"20\">  <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// console.log()</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"21\">  <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// if (ev.target) {</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"22\">  <span class=\"hljs-comment\">//   ev.stopPropagation()</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"23\">  <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// }</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"24\">  <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> target = ev.<span class=\"hljs-property\">target</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">as</span> <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Element</span> | <span class=\"hljs-literal\">null</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"25\">  <span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">console</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">log</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">'xxxxxxxxxxx'</span>, target)</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"26\">  <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (target) {</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"27\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> { x, y, width } = target.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">getBoundingClientRect</span>()</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"28\">    pos.<span class=\"hljs-property\">top</span> = y + <span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">window</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">scrollY</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"29\">    pos.<span class=\"hljs-property\">gap</span> = props.<span class=\"hljs-property\">gap</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"30\">    pos.<span class=\"hljs-property\">x</span> = x + width / <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span> - props.<span class=\"hljs-property\">gap</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"31\">    pos.<span class=\"hljs-property\">w</span> = <span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">window</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">innerWidth</span> - props.<span class=\"hljs-property\">gap</span> * <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span></sp